highlights.text: Linkin Park has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “In the End” is the highest at #22.
“Glorious (feat. Skylar Grey)” by Macklemore and Skylar Grey is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 52 spots at #60.
“That's What I Like” by Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 31 weeks straight.
“In the End” by Linkin Park is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #22.
